author: blair
msg: On the branch for svnserve's --config-file option feature branch,
merge in revisions 24119 and 24121.
The merge conflicts were resolved in the obvious ways, except for the
one in serve.c's find_repos() where the repository's UUID needs to be
copied into the realm, otherwise assertions result when the server
tries to send a realm string to the client to authenticate against.
